				<li><a href="https://twitter.com/DanielHudsonDev" title="Github"><img src="/assets/images/github.svg" width="20" height="20" alt="Github Logo" /></a></li>
				<li><a href="https://twitter.com/DanielHudsonDev" title="Codepen"><img src="/assets/images/codepen.svg" width="20" height="20" alt="Codepen Logo" /></a></li>

			</ul>
		</main>

		<footer>

			<section data-variation="center">

				<div class="cta">

					<h2>Want to find out how i can help you?</h2>

					<p>My inbox is always open if you’re in need of some help and advice, i’ll always try to get back to you.</p>

					<p><a class="button" data-variation="hollow">Get in touch</a></p>

				</div>

			</section>

			<section>
				<p data-variation="tiny">Designed and Developed by Daniel Hudson</p>
			</section>

		</footer>
		
